a code generator tool to make communication between Flutter and the host platform type-safe, easier, and faster  
Currently pigeon supports generating:  
  
Kotlin and Java code for Android  
Swift and Objective-C code for iOS and macOS  
C++ code for Windows  

Add pigeon as a dev_dependency  
@HostApi  
@FlutterApi  

kotlinOut:  
  'android/app/src/main/kotlin/dev/flutter/pigeon_example_app/Messages.g.kt',  
kotlinOptions: KotlinOptions(),  
